<section>
  <div class="section-wraper">
    <div class="section-title">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="section-content">
      <div class="card">
        <h2 class="content-subheading">Introduction</h2>
        <p>
          London Futsal League ("LFL", "we", "us", "our") is committed
          to protecting your personal data and respecting your privacy.
          This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, store, and
          protect your information when you use our website
          (londonfutsalleague.com) and our services.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2 class="content-subheading">Data We Collect</h2>
        <p>We collect the following personal data through our registration and contact forms:</p>
        <ul style="padding-left: 1.5em; margin-top: 0.5em;">
          <li>Full name</li>
          <li>Email address</li>
          <li>Phone number</li>
          <li>Date of birth (solo registration only)</li>
          <li>Postcode / area</li>
          <li>Team information (team registration only)</li>
          <li>Messages submitted via the contact form</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2 class="content-subheading">How We Use Your Data</h2>
        <p>
          The data shared with us through this website will be used
          ONLY for the management of your attendance with LFL futsal
          teams and futsal casual games in London. Specifically, we
          use your data to:
        </p>
        <ul style="padding-left: 1.5em; margin-top: 0.5em;">
          <li>Register you as a player or team in the league</li>
          <li>Contact you about league schedules, fixtures, and updates</li>
          <li>Match solo players with available teams</li>
          <li>Respond to enquiries submitted via the contact form</li>
        </ul>
        <p style="margin-top: 1em;">
          Your data is <strong>not shared with third parties</strong>
          except for the futsal teams participating in the LFL, as
          necessary for league operations.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2 class="content-subheading">Data Storage</h2>
        <p>
          Form submissions are processed via Google Forms and stored
          in Google Sheets. Google's privacy policy and data
          processing terms apply to the storage of this data. We do
          not store your data on any other third-party platforms.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2 class="content-subheading">Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          Our website uses cookies for analytics purposes (Google
          Analytics) and to manage cookie consent (CookieYes).
          Analytics cookies are only activated after you provide
          consent via the cookie banner. You can manage your cookie
          preferences at any time through the cookie settings on our
          website.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2 class="content-subheading">Your Rights</h2>
        <p>Under GDPR, you have the right to:</p>
        <ul style="padding-left: 1.5em; margin-top: 0.5em;">
          <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
          <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
          <li>Withdraw consent for data processing</li>
          <li>Request a copy of your data in a portable format</li>
        </ul>
        <p style="margin-top: 1em;">
          To exercise any of these rights, please contact us at
          <a href="mailto:contact@londonfutsalleague.com">
            contact@londonfutsalleague.com</a>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2 class="content-subheading">Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          If you have any questions about this privacy policy or how
          we handle your personal data, please contact us:
        </p>
        <p style="margin-top: 0.5em;">
          Email:
          <a href="mailto:contact@londonfutsalleague.com">
            contact@londonfutsalleague.com
          </a>
        </p>
        <p>
          Or use our
          <a href="/about.html#contact-us-form">contact form</a>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card" style="border-bottom: none;">
        <p>
          <em>This policy was last updated in March 2026.</em>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
